text: Nikitinka () is a rural locality (a village) in Gafurovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 303 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Tuymazy, 25 km from Duslyk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Nikitinka, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
